{% extends "_base.jinja" %}

{% block main %}
    <div class="row my-3">
        <div class="col-12 py-3">
            <h1 class="text-center noto-bold">
                Welcome to FlightBooker
            </h1>
            <br>
            <h4 class="text-center noto-regular">
                Premiere Air Travel's online booking system
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 py-3">
            <p class="text-center noto-regular">
                Premiere Air Travel is an up-and-coming prestige jet travel provider. We own a range of small but luxurious jets and service a range of routes that
                are neglected by larger carriers, as well as offering a premium and personalised service in exceeding comfort relative to an economy jet - all offered
                with competitive pricing!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row my-3">
        <div class="col-sm-4 p-1">
            <div class="border border-secondary rounded p-3">
                <h4>Routes</h4>
                <p>We currently service 5 different routes, from short flights over to Great Barrier Island, to our premium service all the way over to Sydney. Click here
                to see more details.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4 p-1">
            <div class="border border-secondary rounded p-3">
                <h4>Fleet</h4>
                <p>Our fleet consists of 5 aircraft, across three different models, each catered to suit the particular route it services. We haven't held anything back -
                    all of our aircraft have been purchased brand new and are the premium option in their respective lineup. Click here for more info.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4 p-1">
            <div class="border border-secondary rounded p-3">
                <h4>Book</h4>
                <p>Book a flight, or just see what dates/times we currently offer. Note that you will need to create an account to use our booking service.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endblock %}